A RESOLUTION
1 Recognizing and commending The Association of St. Augustine Alumni-Atlanta; and for
2 other purposes.
3 WHEREAS, The Association of St. Augustine Alumni-Atlanta (ASAAA) is a distinguished
4 network of graduates from St. Augustine's academic programs dedicated to fostering lifelong
5 connections among its members and supporting the institution's mission; and
6 WHEREAS, ASAAA serves as a vital hub for alumni to connect, share experiences, and
7 contribute to the continued growth and success of St. Augustine, ensuring that the impact of
8 its education extends far beyond graduation; and
9 WHEREAS, ASAAA actively engages in charitable initiatives and service projects
10 throughout the Atlanta community, partnering with local schools, shelters, and other
11 organizations in need of support to uphold the spirit of service instilled by St. Augustine; and
12 WHEREAS, the association organizes reunions, networking opportunities, and fundraising
13 events such as charity dinners, silent auctions, and golf tournaments to foster fellowship and
14 generate resources for scholarships, student programs, and institutional needs; and
