15 WHEREAS, through initiatives like The ASAAA Scholarship and Mentorship Fundraiser,
16 ASAAA provides financial aid, mentorship opportunities, and annual college tours to support
17 St. Augustine students as they pursue higher education; and
18 WHEREAS, the association is dedicated to preserving and enhancing the legacy of St.
19 Augustine by encouraging alumni to contribute to the growth of future generations through
20 mentorship, storytelling, and engagement in initiatives that ensure the continuation of the
21 institution's values and traditions; and
22 WHEREAS, it is abundantly fitting and proper that this distinguished organization be
23 appropriately honored during this special time.
24 NOW, THEREFORE, BE IT RESOLVED BY THE HOUSE OF REPRESENTATIVES that
25 the members of this body recognize and commend The Association of St. Augustine
26 Alumni-Atlanta for its exceptional commitment to education, mentorship, and community
27 service and extend best wishes for continued success in its mission.
28 BE IT FURTHER RESOLVED that the Clerk of the House of Representatives is authorized
29 and directed to make an appropriate copy of this resolution available for distribution to The
30 Association of St. Augustine Alumni-Atlanta.
